acme.validation.header.message = The field cannot be empty and must be the correct size
acme.validation.text.message = The field cannot be empty and must be the correct size

acme.validation.ticker.message = Incorrect ticker format. It should be, for example, AA11-ABCDE
acme.validation.audit-report.invalid-period = The start date must be strictly before the end date.
acme.validation.audit-report.not-future = The start date must be in the future.
acme.validation.audit-report.duplicated-ticker.message = An Audit Report with this ticker already exists.

